Interface GaAnalysisContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Configuration, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExpressionContext, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SaAnalysisContext
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GaAnalysisContextImpl, SaAnalysisContextImpl

    public interface GaAnalysisContext
extends Configuration, ExpressionContext
    A representation of the model object 'Ga Analysis Context'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Context
    • Workload
    • Platform
